    "content": "<p>Which of the following, number of lone pair at central atom zero $$\\mathrm{XeO}_3, \\mathrm{XeO}_2 \\mathrm{~F}_2, \\mathrm{XeO}_4, \\mathrm{XeO}_3 \\mathrm{~F}_2, \\mathrm{XeF}_6$$ ?</p>",
    "options": [
      {
        "identifier": "A",
        "content": "2"
      },
      {
        "identifier": "B",
        "content": "3"
      },
      {
        "identifier": "C",
        "content": "4"
      },
      {
        "identifier": "D",
        "content": "Zero"
      }
    ],
    "correct_options": [
      "A"
    ],
    "answer": null,
    "explanation": "<p>Structure of $$\\mathrm{XeO}_4$$ and $$\\mathrm{XeO}_3 \\mathrm{F}_2$$ do not have any lone pair at central-atom. i.e.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m0f89jse/4a4ce3b6-f447-4ed6-8281-a9606dd64952/7bf108e0-65fd-11ef-9de2-c9be9960e8b4/file-jaoe38c1m0f89jsf.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m0f89jse/4a4ce3b6-f447-4ed6-8281-a9606dd64952/7bf108e0-65fd-11ef-9de2-c9be9960e8b4/file-jaoe38c1m0f89jsf.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"AIIMS 2019 Chemistry - Chemical Bonding and Molecular Structure Question 4 English Explanation 1\"></p>\n<p>Thus, option (a) is the correct.\nWhile in $$\\mathrm{XeO}_3, \\mathrm{XeO}_2 \\mathrm{~F}_2$$ and $$\\mathrm{XeF}_6$$ one lone pair of electrons is present on central atom of each compound.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m0f8b5fz/85492765-eac0-4d90-8142-4e690b402098/a87a8df0-65fd-11ef-9de2-c9be9960e8b4/file-jaoe38c1m0f8b5g0.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m0f8b5fz/85492765-eac0-4d90-8142-4e690b402098/a87a8df0-65fd-11ef-9de2-c9be9960e8b4/file-jaoe38c1m0f8b5g0.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"AIIMS 2019 Chemistry - Chemical Bonding and Molecular Structure Question 4 English Explanation 2\"></p>",
