    "explanation": "<p>The structure of $$\\mathrm{IF}_7$$ is pentagonal bipyramidal.</p>\n<p>It can be depicted as follow</p>\n<p>($$Z=53$$) (Ground state) $$=$$</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m3o8t24a/f76ddf89-ff8a-4bc2-9d89-0f4164112ab0/4e74d5a0-a657-11ef-a4a0-dbe08b0b7be0/file-jaoe38c1m3o8t24b.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m3o8t24a/f76ddf89-ff8a-4bc2-9d89-0f4164112ab0/4e74d5a0-a657-11ef-a4a0-dbe08b0b7be0/file-jaoe38c1m3o8t24b.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"AIIMS 2018 Chemistry - Chemical Bonding and Molecular Structure Question 1 English Explanation 1\"></p>\n<p>I (Excited state) =</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m3o8t01u/19409343-9499-43ef-932b-e53d85707a5a/4cdbe620-a657-11ef-a4a0-dbe08b0b7be0/file-jaoe38c1m3o8t01v.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m3o8t01u/19409343-9499-43ef-932b-e53d85707a5a/4cdbe620-a657-11ef-a4a0-dbe08b0b7be0/file-jaoe38c1m3o8t01v.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"AIIMS 2018 Chemistry - Chemical Bonding and Molecular Structure Question 1 English Explanation 2\"></p>\n<p>Here, $$X$$ denotes electrons of $$\\mathrm{F}$$-atoms. The structure of $$\\mathrm{IF}_7$$ is shown below :</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m3o8vcrn/08491aeb-0a4c-429c-af8b-59acaf239331/8e4cfb30-a657-11ef-a4a0-dbe08b0b7be0/file-jaoe38c1m3o8vcro.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m3o8vcrn/08491aeb-0a4c-429c-af8b-59acaf239331/8e4cfb30-a657-11ef-a4a0-dbe08b0b7be0/file-jaoe38c1m3o8vcro.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertic